## fury network is the boutique blockchain for the energy industry!
This online IDE (integrated development enviornment) can be used to design and test applications based on the **STROM**DAO [energyblockchain](https://github.com/energychain/Docker-EnergyChainNode) using html or javascript.
The **STROM**DAO [business object](https://github.com/energychain/StromDAO-BusinessObject) is loaded with each application by default.

## fury network makes it possible for the first time to program new energy blockchain applications directly from the browser

### Happy hacking! Your **STROM**DAO team!

